/|language=Slovenian|title=Povr\u0161inske vode|trans-title=Surface waters}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|Municipality of Dol pri Ljubljani|2007}}|publisher=[[Dol pri Ljubljani|Dol pri Ljubljani Municipality]]|url=http://www.dol.si/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=23&Itemid=35|title=Presentation of the municipality|date=15 December 2007}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|HESS (Projekti)}}|publisher=Hidroelektrarne na spodnji Savi|url=http://www.he-ss.si/projekti.html|title=Projekti|trans-title=Projects|language=Slovenian}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|WFFC|2012}}|url=http://www.wffc-slovenia2012.com/eng/competition/riversavabohinjka.php|title=River Sava Bohinjka (Sector I)|publisher=Fishing Association of Slovenia|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120619020324/http://www.wffc-slovenia2012.com/eng/competition/riversavabohinjka.php|archivedate=19 June 2012|df=dmy-all}}\n*{{cite journal|ref={{harvid|SURS|2002}}|journal=Statistical Yearbook of the Republic of Slovenia|issn=1318-5403|issue=41|title=Territory and climate|url=http://www.stat.si/letopis/2002/01-02.pdf|at=Rivers, longer than 25 km, and their catchment areas|year=2002|publisher=[[Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia]]}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|Zagreb Holding}}|publisher=[[Zagreb Holding]]|url=http://www.sportskiobjekti.hr/default.aspx?id=117#|title=R\u0160C Jarun|trans-title=Recreational and Sports Centre Jarun|language=Serbo-Croatian}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|BMG}}|publisher=BMG Bosanska medijska grupa|url=http://www.vodic.ba/bih/rijeke/sava|title=Sava|language=Serbo-Croatian|trans-title=Sava}}\n*{{GeoQuelle|Sava|||ref=no}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|GCO|June 2011}}|publisher=Government Communication Office (Slovenia)| date=June 2011 |url=http://www.ukom.gov.si/fileadmin/ukom.gov.si/pageuploads/dokumenti/Publikacije/2011/SLOVENIAsymbols_web.pdf|title=Slovenian Symbols}}\n*{{cite web|ref={{harvid|MMATI|2008}}|url=http://www.mppi.hr/UserDocsImages/srednjorocni%20%20plan.pdf|publ