y:The Strokes albums]]\n[[Category:Albums recorded at Shangri-La (recording studio)]]\n[[Category:New wave albums by American artists]]\n[[Category:Electronic albums by American artists]]\n", "name_user": "Nbdelboy", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_New_Abnormal"}
